today was good. 
shawn and i watched detriot rock city.
:)

hate me, i seriously want gwen stefani's cd. 


HEY KIM : today i bought a coke and when i looked under the cap I WON. no drink coke and play again for me hahaha

today was a bust. i had no luck at any thrift stores in st. augustine. still sick and it sucks. i'm car-less until at least wednesday if not forever. sorry for the whining, i'm done. there are some good things i have to look forward to which are as follows: lorna's dinner, prada shoes, having money, and hanging out. 

aaaand scene.

maria bonita's, shoes i've been wanting forever being knocked down to 10$, and south park rule. oh, and the thing made to stretch shoes is majorly underrated. it is the best thing ever. everyone (ok, maybe just girls) should invest in one. and the robot devil from futurama rules too.

well, im glad soda spill day is coming to an end, i guess there should be a catch when a 3 liter costs 99 cents. 

i feel like my vote means nothing. fuck this.


off to dream of kate spade shoes...

went to saw last night (see saw??) it gets my approval.

so i want to do something fun on halloween. people, lets get on that.

its cooler outside than it is in my house. 84 degrees. i feel like my body has been turned inside out.




baby dont like tea?

i love that blue shirt with the little cows on it that landon on the real world wears. i watch the show just to see it.


ps, is livejournal being an asshole to anyone else??

my weekend was quite pleasant.
i love my life.

everything makes me smile. except this cold.
<3a

<lj-cut text="maybe"> I'm a little bit over my head
I come undone at the things he said 
And he's so funny in his bright red shirt
We were all in love and we all got hurt 
I sneak into his car's black leather seat 
The smell of gasoline in the summer heat 
Boy, we're going way too fast 
It's all too sweet to last 

It's alright
And I put myself in his hands
But I hold on to your secrets in white houses
Love, or something ignites in my veins 
And I pray it never fades in white houses<lj-cut>

today was jawsome, i got 3 new bags, a paisley tippit, and a blazer. all for scrubbing some toilets. it was way worth it. in other news, i'm really grateful for all the friends that i have. even if i don't show it, i love each and every one of you very much. especially you. and you, and yes,even you. It's a luscious mix of words and tricks That let us bet when you know we should fold

1. you live really close to me and we had joint custody of knubby even though he loved me more.

2. everything is funny with you and we can talk for hooouuurrs. we've been through alot and have always been there for eachother. AAAANNNDD SCENE

3. you loved the trooper, crazy dr. dave, and all of our early high school adventures. you were on the phone with me when one of my animals died. hung tai forever.

4. i love you even though you make fun of the way i sleep, ok, the way i do everything. i am your retarded baby. you are the gas man. you love my paintings.

5. i am not allowed to watch top gun because of you. now eat the drop and remember, laces out, dan.

6. we have an upcoming new years resolution together.you get me. we must talk all the time or else its a sad day. te amo. degrassi for life. no sad faces allowed.  

7. you listen to usher with me and always always alllwwaayys give me rides. i love you and want to hang out more.

8. we used to talk alot and now you are never online. we share a love for heavyweights. we still need to go shopping in orlando.

9. the thought of you makes me smile soo big. you are so wonderful and i love you more than you know. i miss your driveway and your brother.

10. you were in tv prod and you were one of the few i actually thought had great potential. you have never been mean and you always give me a high five. 

11. you enjoy making fun of me. ive known you for too long. DENNNYYYYSSSS

12. MIGHT BE. we went to high school together and you live next to number 9. 

13. you work with number 4 and you were eating a star crunch today. i wish we were better friends because i think you are awesome.

14. people always think i'm you. you are one of the nicest people i know. you always make me smile.

15. you always make me laugh and i don't think its on purpose. ive seen you naked many times. you need to hang out with me and kim soon.

holy shit i got a callback from the head phlebotanist today and i have an interview tomorrow and i am oh so nervous. wish me luuuck.

the hurricane was overrated at best, the hospital had uncomfortable floors. the cool part was oreo ice cream bars and MEXI-cat. 

when i got home my monitor decided to be a douche and the bulb and/or tube broke so now i am using a 1993 one that gives me a headache but at least i can use it.

i love run on sentences and i hate you if you don't as well.
I'm so impatient I can't stand the wait
mindlessness(is that a word?) and imagination. ha ha ha ha ha ha ha ha

booya

i might have a job  !!

yesterday was ehh, but justin made my night.
early morning/today was excellent and
i dont know why
im updating.
bizzarro.

so its like this.
if its not between the hours of 5ish-11sh pm, you probably wont catch me online. for maybe 3 weeks. for anyone who will actually miss me online, you have my dad to thank. you can call me though.. 3222049 because i have nothing to do everyday, all day now.

having colorless eyes makes me special.
